Loved it!! I only bought it for 2 movies but loved all 4!

Two of the movies were so-so, but two were fun enough to watch several times! However, both DVDs (two movies on each, and you don't have to turn them over) would not pick up where they left off if you had to stop watching and turn off the DVD player. I had to use the remote to open and close the tray before the DVD would load. Then it would pick up where it had been stopped. I thought it was just one DVD that was defective, but this was the case with both. Anyway, not a big deal; just a minor annoyance.
Great movies!!
as advertised

Great news for the hearing impaired! Every one of these movies are English subtitled! More good news! These 4 excellent movies are on 2 discs. You chose which movie you want to watch from the menu. Now sit back, munch your popcorn and enjoy! Oh, for the more sensitive viewers, you might get out a big box of tissues. These movies have "those" kind of moments.
Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind is my favorite movie of the set as Jim Carrey delivered an astounding and mature performance for his role as Joel Barish. Will watch the movie again and again.
good value - I purchased it for one of the four, liked one of the other 3, cheaper than any of them individually.
Love this pack of movies for the price!

This is an odd collection of films, but it is currently the only way to get Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind (one of my favorite films) in plain old DVD format with Prime shipping.  I haven't watched the other films, because they really don't appeal to me, but Sunshine is a quirky classic.
For anyone that has ever lost a loved one to suicide Robin Williams gives a little hope on the subject. Ironic really.
All of the movies play perfectly. Once you insert a disc, two movie titles will appear on the screen, you simply choose the movie you wish to watch and there it is.
Good deal, A+++
